cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.HC

This paper deals with the security and privacy aspects of web browsing, specifically the detection of spying browser extensions. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves machine learning techniques for detection, which could fall under cs.SE (Software Engineering) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The study also involves the collection and analysis of user data, which could be relevant to cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
